Description :
The Patient Billing Strip generator is a small little program designed to help my father track, modify, and manage his "Billing Strips". Perhaps others can use it too! Even if it's just for the patient tracking part.
If you need any help, have any questions, comments, or suggestions, or anything else, please contact me at Igtampe@gmail.com
